Postcode lookup

Lookup a postcode.

postcode_lookup(postcode)

Arguments

postcode

A string. Valid UK postcode.

Value

A list. Returns all available data if found. Returns 404 if postcode does not exist.

Examples

postcode_lookup("EC1Y8LX")
#> $status
#> [1] 200
#> 
#> $result
#> $result$postcode
#> [1] "EC1Y 8LX"
#>
